*Iron Raptor rips and shreds at Rampage, she was bleeding now but she didn't 
care!*

" Didn't your mother teach you to never say NEVER!!!"

* Iron Raptor bites down hard onto Rampage's back and sinks her teeth into a 
deadly lock, she was running out of energy and needed a boost.
She began to extract energy from the Predacon through her teeth as she 
injected a natural poison into his body.
She felt very weak and nearly let go of him but she kept sinking her teeth 
in deeper and deeper. The pain from Rampage's claws were only making it 
harder for her to stand and take his attacks.
They were at a stalemate!*
